{"word":"G4861 - σύμψυχος - sýmpsychos - soom'-psoo-khos - Like-minded","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σύμψυχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sýmpsychos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom'-psoo-khos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Like-minded</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஏகசிந்தையுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"of one mind, of one accord"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>; <i>co-spirited</i>, that is, <i>similar in sentiment:</i> - like-minded.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}